               <lb facs="#facs_3_tr_1_tl_2" n="N002"/>17. <rs type="keyword" ref="#Family">Family </rs>and <rs type="keyword" ref="#Sex">sex</rs> relations.
               <lb facs="#facs_3_tr_1_tl_3" n="N003"/>(Historical relativity. The two meanings of sex)
